-- WestLB, BayernLB Merger Plan Set to Fall Through, FT Deutschland Reports
-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 2010-11-04T05:42:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-04/westlb-bayernlb-merger-plan-set-to-fall-through-ft-deutschland-reports.html
A planned merger between German
state-owned lenders  WestLB AG  and  Bayerische Landesbank  is
faltering and negotiations are likely to be halted soon,
Financial Times Deutschland reported, without saying how it
obtained the information or giving a reason for the breakdown.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  